        <item>
            <title>鄭秀文演唱會現假門票　紙質、字體、二維碼、雷射防偽標籤像真度高</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/you-mi/hottopic/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=you-mi</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/you-mi/hottopic/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 07:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活娛樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[鄭秀文]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[鄭秀文演唱會]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1252029</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">「You &amp; Mi 鄭秀文世界巡迴演唱會香港站」於本月 12 日開鑼，警方接獲市民報案，指有市民表演場館外及網上買到假門票。警方於早前採取行動，「以欺騙手段取得財產」的罪名拘捕 5 名內地男子。警方表示，假門票仿真度十分高，呼籲市民小心提防。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1252031 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240723at-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240723at-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/screenshot20240723at.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲警方表示，假門票仿真度十分高，呼籲市民小心提防（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/v/wiEP8MKk42fJfiWW/"><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs xlh3980 xvmahel x1n0sxbx x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xi81zsa"><span class="html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs"><span class="xt0psk2">香港警察 Hong Kong Police</span></span></span></a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">警方接獲市民報案，指有人在網上及表演場館外兜售假演唱會門票，分別可以用現金或網上轉賬方式購買，惟進場時才被告知門票失效。警方指，假門票仿真度十分高，假門票模仿大量官方門票防偽特徵，包括紙質、字體、二維碼、雷射防偽標籤等。警方亦有發現假門票印上了相同座位編號，而騙徒會主動與買家提出現場交易和驗票，企圖獲受害人信任。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1252033 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13_12-694x349.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="349" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13_12-694x349.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/13_12.jpg 892w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1252034 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/15_11-694x296.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="296" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/15_11-694x296.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/15_11.jpg 929w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1252035 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/17_12-694x387.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="387" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/17_12-694x387.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/17_12.jpg 944w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲假門票模仿大量官方門票防偽特徵，包括紙質、字體、二維碼、雷射防偽標籤等（圖片來源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2012749/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%84%AD%E7%A7%80%E6%96%87%E4%B8%96%E5%B7%A1%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E7%8F%BE%E5%81%87%E9%A3%9B-%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F%E5%BA%A6%E9%AB%98-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1-8000-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%985%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7%E6%B6%89%E8%A9%90%E9%A8%99">星島日報</a>）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">警方 19 日於演唱會場館外當場拘捕持雙程證疑犯及另外四名中國籍男同黨，年齡 34 至 46 歲，他們涉嫌「以欺騙手段取得財產」，暫獲準保釋候查。警方提醒市民，勿輕易相信騙徒驗票方法，亦需提防非官方渠道購買各類型活動門票，及避免向不明來歷的人士購買門票。</p><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/v/wiEP8MKk42fJfiWW/"><span class="x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs xlh3980 xvmahel x1n0sxbx x6prxxf xvq8zen xo1l8bm xi81zsa"><span class="html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs"><span class="xt0psk2">香港警察 Hong Kong Police</span></span></span></a>、<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2012749/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%84%AD%E7%A7%80%E6%96%87%E4%B8%96%E5%B7%A1%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E7%8F%BE%E5%81%87%E9%A3%9B-%E4%BB%BF%E7%9C%9F%E5%BA%A6%E9%AB%98-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1-8000-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%985%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7%E6%B6%89%E8%A9%90%E9%A8%99">星島日報</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/23/you-mi/hottopic/">鄭秀文演唱會現假門票　紙質、字體、二維碼、雷射防偽標籤像真度高</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
