            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Toyota]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1251857</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">豐田 Toyota 展示了他們在非汽車領域上的研究，最新研發的健康座椅聲稱可以只透過坐著就能鍛鍊。這張搖搖晃晃的座椅能讓坐著的人在無意間保持持續的運動，目的是喚醒人類失去了的能力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251867 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251872 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_6e-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_6e-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_6e.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://toyotatimes.jp/en/series/beyondmobility/018.html">Toyota Times</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">這張座椅下有三個支撐柱，其中一個比其他支撐柱短，所以坐著時會有微微的傾斜。三個支撐柱會旋轉，不斷改變座椅 360 度的傾斜方向。支撐柱的旋轉緩慢，需要超過 1 分鐘，坐著的人幾乎不會留意到傾斜。座椅的原理是出於人類與生俱來的「姿勢反射」，會在傾斜中下意識維持身體的姿勢，所以坐在座椅上時會自然移動骨盆，而頭部保持不動。即使坐著，肌肉也會反覆緊張和放鬆，有助於減輕長途開車時的腰痠背痛。座椅的效果類似於訓練核心的平衡球，不同的是它能夠自動 360 度旋轉。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_20113"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tTnZWctxc44?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1251870 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_4_-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_4_-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/series_design_018_4_-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://toyotatimes.jp/en/series/beyondmobility/018.html">Toyota Times</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Toyota 表示你會在坐這個座椅大約 20 分鐘後感到疲倦，代表你正在使用不常用的肌肉。前沿研究中心量子人類研究小組專案經理 Tadashi Odashima 提到以前的日本人可攜帶 100 kg 的米包，反映的不是以前的人有多厲害，而是現代人的退步。這張座椅有望促進肌肉協調，喚醒以前失去了的能力，加強那些不能像肌肉或大腦那樣有意識地訓練的領域。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://toyotatimes.jp/en/series/beyondmobility/018.html">Toyota Times</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/toyota-bz3c%e3%80%81bz4x-ev-suv-china/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">豐田 bz3c、bz3x 電動 SUV   北京車展現身主攻年輕市場</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/toyota-new-chair-enhancement-by-recovering-inherent-abilities/fun-tech/">豐田 Toyota 研發新型健康座椅　僅靠坐著就能做運動改善腰痠背痛</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
