            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Wi-Fi 7]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1248810</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>隨著現代生活中對高速網絡的需求日益增加，家中的網絡設備承受著前所未有的壓力。無論是在家辦公時需要高清視像會議、享受 4K/8K 串流媒體播放 HDR 影片、享受 Hi-Res 音樂，或是玩網上遊戲、使用 AR/VR 裝置等，對網絡頻寬和穩定性的要求也愈來愈高。如果你需要更快更穩定的網絡連接設備，就要考慮購置 Wi-Fi 7 裝置。今次我們會實測 NETGEAR 近日推出的 Nighthawk 系列最新產品：RS300 Wi-Fi 7 路由器。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249316" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00566-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00566-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00566.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Nighthawk RS300 是 NETGEAR 最新推出的 Wi-Fi 7 路由器，速度比 Wi-Fi 6 快 2.4 倍。Nighthawk RS300 最高支援 100 個裝置連接，適合需要使用多裝置的重度網絡使用者。</p><h2>機身設計簡約　六角設計</h2><p>今次評測的 NETGEAR Nighthawk RS 300 路由器外觀設計線條簡約，機身採用六角形設計，放在家中不顯突兀，。今代外殼採用不反光磨沙麪塑膠，簡單不失典雅之餘亦有效防止外殼留下指紋，兼顧美觀及實用。<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249318" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00022-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00022-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00022.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249347" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00028-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00028-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00028.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249364" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00041-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00041-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00041.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2></h2><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/netgear-orbi-970-2/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】NETGEAR Orbi 970　旗艦級 Wi-Fi 7 + 覆蓋範圍可達一萬呎</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/netgear-july/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 七月優惠推介    Nighthawk WiFi 7 路由器 RS300 全新登場</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/netgear-event-2024june/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 快閃優惠　買指定商品可半價換購智能相架</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>機身多個連接口　方便用家按需求連接</h2><p>路由器具備 1 個 2.5 Gbps 網路埠和 2 個 2.5Gbps 以太網 LAN 埠，另設 2 個 1000Mbps 以太網 LAN 埠，方便用户接駁遊戲機、電腦、IoT 裝置等高速上網。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00042-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00042-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00042.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲主機設有 1 個 2.5 Gbps 網路埠，和 2 個 2.5Gbps 以太網 LAN 埠</p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kan00005-694x462.avif 694w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/kan00005.avif 1280w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture></p><h2></h2><h2>安裝簡易　一 App 完成</h2><p>Nighthawk RS300 的安裝非常簡單，。為顧及新手，Netgear 推出了 Nighthawk 專用應用程式，用户只需連接電源和 LAN 線後下載 Nighthawk 專用 App，掃描路由器的 QR Code，，其後的手續就可交由應用程式自動設置。用户還可以通過 App 進行網絡管理，包括暫停互聯網、進行網速測試、追蹤網絡數據使用量，設置單獨的訪客網絡等，讓網絡管理變得輕鬆便捷。</p><picture><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249363" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00025-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00025-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00025.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲隨附的配件</p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987-268x580.avif 268w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987.avif 416w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1228794 sp-no-webp" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987-268x580.jpeg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987-268x580.jpeg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827987.jpeg 416w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲下載「NETGEAR Nighthawk」應用程式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1179926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1.png 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲註冊「NETGEAR」帳户</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1179926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1-416x900.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/netgear1.png 591w" alt="" width="268" height="580" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲註冊「NETGEAR」帳户</p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279871-268x580.avif 268w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo17128279871.avif 416w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249278" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇你的產品，小編手上的是 Nighthawk Wi-Fi 路由器</p><picture><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249279" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-1.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲掃描路由器的 QR Code</p><picture><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249361" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00034-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00034-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kan00034.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲路由器的 QR Code</p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991-268x580.avif 268w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991.avif 416w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></picture><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991-268x580.avif 268w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/photo1712827991.avif 416w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249280" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-2.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲Netgear Nighthawk 應用程式會自動替你完成剩下的步驟，此時需要按「加入」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249289" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-7-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-7-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-7.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p>等手機連接到路由器便可直接上網了。用户事後如果想調整任何設定，亦可利用 Nighthawk 手機 App 遙距管理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1249293" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-8-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-8-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/photo_60868796901712-8.jpg 416w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲看見這個頁面就代表已經完成掃描所有衞星子機</p><h2>網速測試</h2><p>NETGEAR Nighthakw RS300 是 Wi-Fi 7 裝置，能夠連接更多裝置，覆蓋範圍和網絡表現更佳。我們在辦公室進行實際測試，嘗試在複雜環境下如何解決無線網絡訊號問題。</p><p>首先我們在支援 Wi-Fi 7 的手提電腦使用「Speedtest」網絡測速軟件，距離路由器 1 米範圍內測得下載 2,344 Mbps，上載 2,130 Mbps，延遲 3 ms。</p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsappimage2024052-291x580.avif 291w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/whatsappimage2024052.avif 452w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 291px" /></picture><picture><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251839" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-443x580.jpeg" alt="" width="443" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-443x580.jpeg 443w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072.jpeg 636w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 443px" /></picture><p style="text-align: center;">▲離路由器 1 米內（沒有牆壁阻隔）</p><p>小編在沒有牆壁阻隔的情況下，距離路由器約 5 米再使用測速軟件，測得下載 2,007 Mbps，上載 1,457 Mbps，延遲仍能夠保持在 4 ms。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251843" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-4-433x580.jpeg" alt="" width="433" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-4-433x580.jpeg 433w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-4.jpeg 617w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 433px" />▲離路由器 5 米的測試結果（沒有牆壁阻隔）</p><p>小編這次在隔住一面牆，遠離路由器 10 米的情況下使用測速軟件，下載錄得 1,238 Mbps，上載 918 Mbps，延遲 4 ms，即使隔住一面牆，表現仍然令人滿意。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1251844" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-5-441x580.jpeg" alt="" width="441" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-5-441x580.jpeg 441w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/whatsappimage2024072-5.jpeg 627w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 441px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲離路由器 10 米的測試結果（中間有一面牆）</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/netgear-orbi-970-2/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】NETGEAR Orbi 970　旗艦級 Wi-Fi 7 + 覆蓋範圍可達一萬呎</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/netgear-july/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 七月優惠推介    Nighthawk WiFi 7 路由器 RS300 全新登場</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/netgear-event-2024june/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 快閃優惠　買指定商品可半價換購智能相架</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>總結：平玩 Wi-Fi 7</h2><p>NETGEAR Nighthawk RS300 路由器以其 Wi-Fi 7 技術、高達 9.3Gbps 的速度、廣泛的覆蓋範圍和強大的安全防護，提供了穩定且高效的網絡連接。其設計簡約，且安裝簡便，適閤家庭和小型辦公室使用。Nighthawk RS300 提供高性能、穩定且安全的網絡連接，可供需要此類功能的用户考慮。如果你的裝置支援 Wi-Fi 7，使用 Nighthakw RS300 後就可以享受高速連線。</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/27/netgear-orbi-970-2/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】NETGEAR Orbi 970　旗艦級 Wi-Fi 7 + 覆蓋範圍可達一萬呎</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/15/netgear-july/wireless-home/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 七月優惠推介    Nighthawk WiFi 7 路由器 RS300 全新登場</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/netgear-event-2024june/wireless-home/routers/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">NETGEAR 快閃優惠　買指定商品可半價換購智能相架</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/netgear-nighthawk-rs300/wireless-home/routers/">【評測】NETGEAR Nighthawk RS300　平玩 Wi-Fi7 + 設單獨訪客網絡</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
